 by adapting online to real-time wind velocity.\nNumerical results show that our optimized trajectory can better adapt to\nvarious setups with different target data volume and buoys' topology as well as\nvarious wind speed/direction/variance compared with benchmark schemes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Dec 2021 15:29:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-28"}
